- Rudi Pendavingh, Stefan van Zwam (2013-04-01): initial version

TESTS::

    sage: from sage.matroids.advanced import *
    sage: M = CircuitClosuresMatroid(matroids.named_matroids.Fano())
    sage: TestSuite(M).run()

